text: Jeffrey Lynn Collins (born December 19, 1955) is a Republican member of the North Carolina General Assembly.http://votesmart.org/candidate/biography/117808/jeffrey- collins#.VWu9cmTBzGc He represents the 25th district. ==Honors== In 2018, Collins was listed as a Champion of the Family in the NC Values Coalition Scorecard. ==References== Category:Living people Category:North Carolina Republicans Category:21st-century American politicians Category:1955 births
title: Jeff Collins (North Carolina politician)
